channel.title: Pretty good song, for me at least
channel.description: Well, listening to some Alice Cooper and watching some vids on YouTube, I listened to I'm Eighteen about 4 times, I really love it now. Listen to the lyrics, oh by the way, I've had it in my head all day, one of the rare occasions where I like the song playing in my head. ;D
